100
00:07:08,540 --> 00:07:11,520
If you want to have hot pot, we'll have hot pot.

101
00:07:12,180 --> 00:07:14,480
Let's invite Zhan Zhi Lin, too.

102
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:17,620
I'll ask him but I don't think he'll come.

103
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:20,480
Well, too bad for him then.

104
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:22,020
A lot of people are coming tomorrow.

105
00:07:22,020 --> 00:07:24,100
You need to go shopping with me.

106
00:07:24,100 --> 00:07:25,600
As you wish.

107
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:28,460
- We're going back now. 
 - Bye, Lord Bao.

108
00:07:28,460 --> 00:07:30,520
- Bye-bye. 
 - Bye.

109
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:40,060
Hello, Sister Shan.

110
00:07:40,060 --> 00:07:43,070

111
00:07:55,380 --> 00:07:58,280
Hello. My name is Zheng Feng.

112
00:07:58,280 --> 00:08:00,320
I'm the creator of this painting.

113
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:03,780
What's the name of this painting?

114
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:06,860
"Silhouette."

115
00:08:06,860 --> 00:08:09,160
It's the silhouette of a lover.

116
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:13,260
Seems like you're really fond of painting women's silhouettes.

117
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:15,980
Thank you.

118
00:08:15,980 --> 00:08:18,900
You seem to be interested in my paintings too.

119
00:08:18,900 --> 00:08:23,900
I'm very honored that I collected one of them many years ago.

120
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:30,680
Why would you have this painting?

121
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:33,679
Liang Shu Qian, do you still remember her?

122
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:37,359
You are... her son？

123
00:08:37,359 --> 00:08:40,760
Liang Shu Qian committed suicide because of you.

124
00:08:41,819 --> 00:08:44,019
Because of me?

125
00:08:44,019 --> 00:08:46,679
Your dad asked you to look for me, right?

126
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:48,140
It's been so many years.

127
00:08:48,140 --> 00:08:51,160
It's about time to clear up this misunderstanding.

128
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,560
Misunderstanding?

129
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:55,340
What misunderstanding?

130
00:08:55,340 --> 00:08:58,860
Your mom and I were just like-minded on an artistic level.

131
00:08:58,860 --> 00:09:01,420
It wasn't what your dad thought it was.

132
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:04,920
Don't start with me.

133
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:07,760
Why? Don't you dare admit it?

134
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:14,380
Your mom only came here to learn how to paint and kill time.

135
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:18,060
Do you see these paintings of mine?

136
00:09:18,060 --> 00:09:20,260
They are very similar, right?

137
00:09:20,260 --> 00:09:21,560
That's right.

138
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:23,700
They are all paintings of your mom.

139
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:25,420
But,

140
00:09:29,980 --> 00:09:32,660
your dad was the subject of all your mom's paintings.

141
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:39,660
If what you said is true,

142
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:45,300
why did my dad tell me she committed suicide because you abandoned her?

143
00:09:45,300 --> 00:09:47,420
She didn't even love me!

144
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:49,920
Why would she commit suicide for me?

145
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:52,860
That's just your dad's speculation, okay?

146
00:09:53,820 --> 00:09:58,620
Your mom contacted me before she passed away.

147
00:09:58,620 --> 00:10:01,760
She saw the texts your dad sent to Tian Cai Yun

148
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:04,040
and couldn't accept the reality.

149
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:08,860

150
00:10:08,860 --> 00:10:12,720
He also lied and claimed your mom had an affair.

151
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,780
These are the texts

152
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:26,440
your mom sent before she died.

153
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:28,540
Without these things,

154
00:10:28,540 --> 00:10:33,740
the two of us will be misunderstood forever.

155
00:10:51,940 --> 00:10:54,340
Before my mom passed away,

156
00:10:54,340 --> 00:10:57,560
 did you text Tian Cai Yun and tell her you'll take care of her and her son?

157
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:59,480
How do you know?

158
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:03,740
There was nothing between Mom and Zheng Feng.

159
00:11:03,740 --> 00:11:05,780
What exactly did Zheng Feng tell you?

160
00:11:05,780 --> 00:11:07,780
Your mom didn't love me anymore.

161
00:11:07,780 --> 00:11:10,460
She was the one who asked me for a divorce.

162
00:11:10,460 --> 00:11:14,000
 That's because she couldn't accept the fact that you were going to take care of Tian Cai Yun.

163
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:16,260
Every time she went to learn to paint from Zheng Feng,

164
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,960
she painted you every time.

165
00:11:19,640 --> 00:11:22,060
She never got over you.

166
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:25,940
 If you didn't love her, why didn't you tell her earlier?

167
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:32,200
Why did you cause her so much pain?

168
00:11:32,860 --> 00:11:35,860
 It's fine if you felt sorry for Tian Cai Yun and took care of her and her son.

169
00:11:35,860 --> 00:11:38,920
 But why did you have to say

170
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:42,840
 you'd rather get a divorce to take care of Tian Cai Yun for the rest of your life?

171
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:47,380
 Over the years, you've been treating her with a lukewarm attitude.

172
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:51,500
You would rather spend the night in the office than come home.

173
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:54,100
I saw it all with my own eyes.

174
00:11:54,100 --> 00:11:57,840
Mom kept saying kind things about you.

175
00:11:57,840 --> 00:12:00,880
 How can you slander her of having an affair with Zheng Feng first?

176
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:02,740
It was my fault.

177
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:07,700
I didn't expect that.

178
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:11,460
I thought your mom fell in love with someone else.

179
00:12:11,460 --> 00:12:14,540
 I really didn't expect things to turn out like this.

180
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:19,260
 Shu Qian. I have something—

181
00:12:19,260 --> 00:12:21,600
 I want a divorce.

182
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:24,400
 What?

183
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:27,360
 I want a divorce.

184
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,860
 Why?

185
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:32,620
 Because I fell in love with someone I shouldn't fall in love with.

186
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:35,160
 As for you,

187
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:39,310
 you did the same thing.

188
00:12:39,880 --> 00:12:44,020
 I was the one she was talking about.

189
00:12:52,130 --> 00:12:55,920

190
00:12:58,440 --> 00:13:00,040
Lift your feet.

191
00:13:08,040 --> 00:13:11,080
I checked it. That place is packed today.

192
