209
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:59,300
Who cares about the quality of your product?

210
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,100
Don't even think about it!

211
00:14:06,100 --> 00:14:10,020
Things like roses or magic will never enter my Happy Family.

212
00:14:10,020 --> 00:14:11,500
I will never do that.

213
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:13,160
I will never do that. Never.

214
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:17,660
I'm telling you, Happy Family will win by our taste.

215
00:14:17,660 --> 00:14:22,420
Well, we have a star.

216
00:14:23,900 --> 00:14:25,300
A star?

217
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:29,120
- You mean Jiang Nan? 
 - That's right.

218
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:30,900
That's right.

219
00:14:32,300 --> 00:14:33,300
Would that be okay?

220
00:14:33,300 --> 00:14:35,820
