221
00:14:35,820 --> 00:14:38,280
- Call him. 
 - Okay.

222
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,560
You can't catch me.

223
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:47,600
- Cheng Cheng, a video call from your dad. 
 - Answer it for me.

224
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:50,640
Uncle, Auntie.

225
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:53,480
Jiang Nan. Where's Cheng Cheng?

226
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:55,780
