229
00:15:00,560 --> 00:15:02,100
Here's the thing.

230
00:15:02,100 --> 00:15:04,900
A restaurant opened across the street from us.

231
00:15:04,900 --> 00:15:07,640
 Big Lin said it's some kind of internet-trendy restaurant.

232
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:09,920
 They stole all our business.

233
00:15:09,920 --> 00:15:13,100
Dad, internet-trendy restaurants rely on the advertisement.

234
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:17,180
If we only judge it by the taste of their food, they probably can't compare to our place.

235
00:15:18,020 --> 00:15:20,380
We can do some advertisements later too.

236
00:15:20,380 --> 00:15:21,840
 That's right, Uncle.

237
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:24,880
Didn't you update the menu and add a lot of specialty dishes?

238
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:27,840
We can promote all of that at the same time.

239
00:15:29,180 --> 00:15:32,680
 Well, there's no need for that. I don't want to bother you.

240
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:34,640
Uncle, no need to be polite with me.

241
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:36,620
It's our family business. There's no trouble at all.

242
00:15:36,620 --> 00:15:38,360
That's what I'm supposed to do.

243
00:15:39,920 --> 00:15:41,160
Thank you.

244
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:43,760
You, young people, have more creative ideas.

245
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:45,460
 Mom, don't worry about it.

246
00:15:45,460 --> 00:15:47,860
Well, that's it then. We're hanging up now.

247
00:15:47,860 --> 00:15:49,660
We're hanging up.

248
00:15:51,040 --> 00:15:53,140
It's done!

249
00:15:54,680 --> 00:15:56,900
Should I do a live streaming at the restaurant?

250
00:15:56,900 --> 00:15:59,780
